- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as camera-projector calibration is often used in robotics applications. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is another possibility as the paper deals with image warping and projection. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a potential category as the paper deals with camera and projector models. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is also a possibility as the paper deals with correspondence algorithms and optimization.
